fi

# ─── Open WebUI: register MiOS docs as a Knowledge collection ──────────
# Walks /usr/share/mios/{ai,docs,cookbooks,hermes,prompts},
# /etc/mios/system-prompts, /CLAUDE.md, /AGENTS.md and registers each
# as an OWUI File row with path = absolute FHS path + a snapshot of
